      <div itemprop="commentText">
       <p><a href="#comment-37"><strong>Kevin:</strong></a> Nevermind — got it to work! I think I needed a valid <code>Info.plist</code> file, and make the script executable underneath the <code>MacOS</code> folder.</p>
